== Spanish ==

=== Etymology ===
From ''[[bastar]]''

=== Adjective ===
'''bastante'''
# more than [[enough]]; [[sufficient]]
#:''Ha llovido '''bastante''' la última semana.'' (It has rained a lot in the last week.)

=== Adverb ===
'''bastante'''
# Enough; [[sufficiently]]
# Fairly [[well]]; to a [[considerable]] degree.
#:''Lo conozco bastante.'' (I know him quite well.)

